’Щ@00e117e3b0dbf65e62340cd98eeccfcfbb94134b1768670513bec3e7b920bfcaЪеTitle: title: metadata access
Path: Examples
Content:
Access metadata and data from a stream together.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> {foo: bar} | to json --raw | metadata access {|meta| {in: $in, content: $meta.content_type}}
